    <Intro
      body="Through the building of the TCNJ Pavilion, the TCNJ community will join together for musical and dramatic performances, lectures and debates, and ceremonies and presentations that spark interdisciplinary connections among learners, researchers, innovators, students, and community members."
      buttonText="Invest in Community"
